er increase in tax breaks the new york times retrieved march     page susan keen judy december   next chapter will bush be able to govern usa today retrieved march     raasch chuck abrams doug september   top congressional leaders rushed to secure location gannett company usa today retrieved march     waller douglas july    questions for jc watts time magazine retrieved march     jenkins ron march   watts capitol visit stirs speculation associated press the edmond sun retrieved march     president bush announced his intention to nominate press release office of the press secretary january   retrieved march     politics and the economy former rep watts opens consulting firm the new york times january   retrieved march     a b meier barry november   exquarterback thrives as lobbyist the new york times retrieved march     watts j c march   well all pay for this massive spending plan las vegas reviewjournal retrieved march     dillards inc announces election of jc watts jr to board of directors business wire dun  bradstreet march   retrieved march     terex corporation elects former congressman jc watts jr to its board business wire dun  bradstreet january   retrieved march     terex corporation elects former congressman jc watts jr to its board business wire february   retrieved march     gopac chairman jc watts jr travels to mississippi for gop campaign events on tuesday september  us newswire september   retrieved march     espo david october   analysis a vote with unforeseen consequences associated press usa today retrieved march     wolf richard december   republicans of  revolution reflect on  usa today retrieved march     andrews helena july   watts launches africanamerican channel the politico retrieved march     black republicans consider voting for obama associated press usa today june   retrieved march     jones del september   board diversity expands political spectrum usa today retrieved march     mcnutt michael may   jc watts vows to decide soon on run the