ris gensman thomas johnson sr morris wickersham morris wickersham johnson jr j smith camp english lucas th district mcclintic massingale wickersham peden wickersham th district morgan swindall herrick garber marland ferguson rizley wilson belcher atlarge murray  thompson weaver rogers territory harvey flynn callahan flynn mcguire v t e iheartmedia corporate officers bob pittman chairmanceo board of directors lowry mays irving azoff b j red mccombs j c watts john h williams radio stations list of radio stations owned by iheartmedia radio networks fox sports radio premiere networks premium choice total traffic and weather network miscellaneous clear channel outdoor clear channel uk iheartradio list of programming syndicated by iheartmedia mediabase radio computing services authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  us congress w retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejcwattsoldid categories  birthsthcentury american politiciansstcentury american politiciansstcentury baptist ministersafricanamerican members of the united states house of representativesafricanamerican players of american footballafricanamerican players of canadian footballafricanamerican people in oklahoma politicsamerican athletepoliticiansamerican football quarterbacksamerican radio executivesbaptist ministers from the united statescanadian football quarterbackscorporation commissioners of oklahomaiheartmedia incliving peoplemembers of the united states house of representatives from oklahomaoklahoma republicansoklahoma sooners football playersottawa rough riders playerspeople from eufaula oklahomaplayers of american football from oklahomarepublican party members of the united states house of representativestoronto argonauts playershidden categories use mdy dates from february pages which use embedded infobox templates with the title parameterpages using infobox officeholder with unknown parametersall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statem